import React from "react"; const MatchupCard = ({ matchup }) => { return (

{matchup.time} {matchup.date}

{matchup.team_1.full_name}

@

{matchup.team_2.full_name}

Win{" "} ${50 * matchup.team_1.money_multiplier.toFixed(2)} on{" "} {matchup.team_1.short_name} win.

Win{" "} ${50 * matchup.team_2.money_multiplier.toFixed(2)} on{" "} {matchup.team_2.short_name} win.

); }; export default MatchupCard;
